Azio’s Retro Classic Bluetooth keyboard is now shipping globally. The device sports a typewriter-style design and is constructed from wood, leather, and metal. It sports Kaihua mechanical keys with per-key backlighting and has a 6,000mAh battery – which can last up to one year with the backlight disabled. The keyboard is charged through a USB Type-C cable and can also be used in a wired configuration. The device is available in four different styles – Onyx, Posh, Artisan, and Elwood. The Bluetooth keyboard is available for $220 from the Azio website. 